  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876670/extras/02fce69b3e74d08d1c4ca86fd3ac8804.avif?t=1654812991\" width=500 height=192 /></span><br>Woodcutter Deluxe Edition is a classic platformer, tells the story of Woodcutter whose child was kidnapped. Embark on a magical adventure through the land of Aaran and help Woodcutter retrieve his firstborn.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>There are 79 levels to complete, filled with coins and enemies,</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>3 weapons to use (Boomerang, Bow, Explosing barrels) and your body to smash your enemies,</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>You can: run, jump, double jump, wall jump, wall slide, swim and more,</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Languages (Polish, English, Russian, German),</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Very long product support is planned!</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876670/extras/02fce69b3e74d08d1c4ca86fd3ac8804.avif?t=1654812991\" width=500 height=192 /></span><br>Woodcutter Deluxe Edition is a classic platformer, tells the story of Woodcutter whose child was kidnapped. Embark on a magical adventure through the land of Aaran and help Woodcutter retrieve his firstborn.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>There are 79 levels to complete, filled with coins and enemies,</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>3 weapons to use (Boomerang, Bow, Explosing barrels) and your body to smash your enemies,</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>You can: run, jump, double jump, wall jump, wall slide, swim and more,</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Languages (Polish, English, Russian, German),</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Very long product support is planned!</li></ul>",
